title: DJ's Updated Top 50 Prospects & Traits Bill Belichick Looks for in Defensive Players
itunes:title: DJ's Updated Top 50 Prospects & Traits Bill Belichick Looks for in Defensive Players
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, DJ gives the updates in his top 50 prospects list and Bucky reacts to it (2:57). To wrap up the show, the pair analyze what traits Patriots head coach Bill Belichick looks for in defensive players (14:01).
